      "text": "え？　どうしたのよ\nせっかくの海なのに、そんな暗い顔して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's sad to say goodbye‚ but it's finally time to end…\nThank you for coming today——",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、体調でも悪いのか？\nそれなら無理せず休んでいた方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6124269324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
